# Estimating throughput needs

## **Recommended documents**

Please refer to our [online documentation](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/cosmos-db/request-units#estimating-throughput-needs) 
for an understanding on how to estimate your throughput needs and ensure that you are following all the performance tips applicable to your application described [here](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/cosmos-db/performance-tips) to avoid high RU charges.
